original_title: M.A Charpentier à la Chapelle Royale de Versailles
overview: An excellent example of French high baroque performed by Le Concert des Nations and La Capella Reial de Catalunya under Jordi Savall's direction at the Royal Chapel of Versailles to commemorete the 310th anniversary of Charpentier’s death.
title: M.A Charpentier at the Royal Chapel of Versailles
